amento (Shime-Waza) são adicionadas ao exame da faixa Marrom?', '["Hadaka-Jime e Okuri-Eri-Jime","Kata-Ha-Jime e Sode-Guruma-Jime","Nami-Juji-Jime e Gyaku-Juji-Jime","Sankaku-Jime e Do-Jime"]'::jsonb, 'Kata-Ha-Jime e Sode-Guruma-Jime', 'technique');